Package com.rvandoosselaer.jmeconverter

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Processor
    A processor for a Model object.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AnimationProcessor
    A processor implementation that migrates the deprecated AnimControl and SkeletonControl to the new AnimComposer and SkinningControl.
    BinaryWriter
    A processor implementation that saves the converted model as a JME binary (.j3o) next to the original model file.
    Converter
    The main starting point of the converter.
    GroovyProcessor
    A processor implementation that loads and runs a groovy file against the supplied model.
    Main
    Starts the converter application and converts the models that are passed as program arguments.
    Model
    Class representing the loaded model.
    ModelLoader
    Class loading the model using JME's AssetManager.
    ModelLogger
    A processor implementation that logs the structure of the model to the configured logger.
    VersionHelper
    Loads the version.properties file that is generated during the gradle build process and exposes version information.
